&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>四月游记</title><link>https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/</link><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/cover.webp" alt="Featured image of post 四月游记" />&lt;h1 id="四月游记">四月游记&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>2024年4月北京旅游记录&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="4月14日">4月14日&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>早上起个大早赶飞机&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-083912.webp"
width="4000"
height="2250"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-083912_hu11594600420792804698.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-083912_hu6845955570908790981.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="航站楼"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>位置选了最后一排双人座，前面都是三人，没想到旁边没人，i人爽到&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-084144.webp"
width="4000"
height="3000"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-084144_hu13771799947047076323.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-084144_hu2963209451855056370.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="座位"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="320px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>第一次真正意义上坐飞机&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-103359.webp"
width="4000"
height="3000"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-103359_hu5162646687020322306.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-103359_hu2867878642924198699.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="窗户"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="320px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>下飞机了，也是第一次坐上摆渡车&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-124935.webp"
width="4000"
height="3000"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-124935_hu13897844957502073465.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-124935_hu7452776907105864608.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="摆渡车"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="320px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>午餐就是飞机餐，下飞机后坐地铁先到民宿休息了下，然后吃晚饭&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>先到第二天的主线任务位置踩点&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-184933.webp"
width="4000"
height="3000"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-184933_hu17703428566391665737.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240414-184933_hu8468558730313524476.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="医院"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="320px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>晚上就在床上看了会电子书&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="4月15日">4月15日&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>早上第一次吃煎饼&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然后赶去医院面试，过啦&lt;/p>
&lt;p>中午回去平复了下心情，补了个觉&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>晚上出去随便走走！&lt;/p>
&lt;p>先去了单推人的大学&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240415-190719.webp"
width="4000"
height="2250"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240415-190719_hu3788143187183255060.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240415-190719_hu1694639777500896881.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Ruby University"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>其实是到了北京在看地图的时候才发现在复试地点隔壁的&lt;/p>
&lt;p>刷身份证就能进，好好好&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然后去了奥体中心&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240415-205529.webp"
width="4000"
height="2250"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240415-205529_hu16760365699821424884.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240415-205529_hu16311904962382968372.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="鸟巢"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>从南到北走了一圈就回来了&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="4月16日">4月16日&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>六点多就醒了&lt;/p>
&lt;p>还是煎饼起手&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-065204.webp"
width="3000"
height="4000"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-065204_hu16518452711077062513.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-065204_hu5562745156993606278.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="煎饼"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>去了天安门&lt;/p>
&lt;p>到天安门西才知道没预约连走路都不行，必须坐地铁原路返回&lt;/p>
&lt;p>后来绕道对面国家大剧院，发现不能走路但是可以骑车&lt;/p>
&lt;p>扫了一辆共享单车，如愿看到了天安门，p人魅力时刻&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-084721.webp"
width="4000"
height="2250"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-084721_hu12725440698346480890.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-084721_hu3775191906558087338.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="天安门"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>然后去了王府井，但是感觉没什么好逛的，可能是太早了&lt;/p>
&lt;p>继续走到了……&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-090835.webp"
width="3000"
height="4000"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-090835_hu10972454894656182346.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-090835_hu5965221609857167913.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="协和"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="75"
data-flex-basis="180px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对面的礼堂&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-090912.webp"
width="3964"
height="2230"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-090912_hu17105659905630002009.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-090912_hu9576771591698440288.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="礼堂"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>之后不知道去哪，上小红书看到了附近有一条步行街叫南锣鼓巷：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-093939.webp"
width="4000"
height="2250"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-093939_hu15871090320332853278.webp 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/240417-apr-travel/img/20240416-093939_hu16365338189126877504.webp 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="南锣鼓巷"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>逛完了回民宿退房的路上收到了航班取消的消息，本来下午还想去地坛玩的，临时改签到下午航班只好马不停蹄赶往机场了&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>没有留下遗憾，因为知道马上就要再来了&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>